suite.doc: For this assignment please use https://test.briqstaging.net, our Funnel application’s staging environment. 1. Explore the mentioned Funnel application. Feel free to play around and test what happens. 2. Design a couple of test scenarios of what you would like to test, based on what you think are the most important things to test. 3. Implement the automated testing of one or more of the scenarios you came up with. 4. Make a short list of what could also be tested but is not described in the second question. 5. Share your implementation and the list with us in a ZIP file or Git repo.
